      <h2>🔭 What's Next for Texas AI Data Centers?</h2>
      <p>Texas is positioned to remain at the center of AI infrastructure growth in the coming years. As more organizations deploy AI at scale, demand for power, land, and connectivity will continue to rise.</p>
      <p>With the right mix of grid planning, community engagement, and energy innovation, Texas can support this growth while balancing reliability, affordability, and sustainability.</p>

